item.description:
@IP-Drowner wrote:

Please stop attaching every file you find. They’re from somewhere else and the owners don’t like it to be re-distributed in its’ form. That error, obviously means that there is a duplicate identifier inside of the script, which the latest SRL Version includes. So it returns the top most identifier That’s why it was located in the includes

But, unfortuantely, i won’t fix up this script since it it clearly out-dated and not working. So, it is best to find another updated script The recommended place for scripts is the SRL Forums
